            ├─ when asset out receiver is set to the zero address
            │  └─ it should revert
            └─ when asset out receiver is not set to the zero address
               ├─ when the fee aggregator is set to the zero address
               │  └─ it should revert
               └─ when the fee aggregator is not set to the zero address
                  ├─ when the maximum discount is set to zero
                  │  └─ it should revert
                  └─ when the maximum discount is not set to zero
                     ├─ when the Cow Protocol Vault Relayer is set to the zero address
                     │  └─ it should revert
                     └─ when the Cow Protocol Vault Relayer is not set to the zero address
                        ├─ when the Cow Protocol Settlement contract is set to the zero address
